1
00:00:32,583 --> 00:00:36,041
I don't understand how
everything got so screwed up...

2
00:00:36,125 --> 00:00:37,833
I wanted to help her...

3
00:00:37,916 --> 00:00:39,750
I didn't wanna fight.

4
00:00:39,833 --> 00:00:41,583
I wanted to help.

5
00:00:41,666 --> 00:00:43,000
That's it.

6
00:00:43,083 --> 00:00:45,458
That's all there is to it.

7
00:00:45,541 --> 00:00:47,375
Then you'll die.

8
00:00:47,458 --> 00:00:49,958
There's no way you'll
survive this next attack...

9
00:00:50,041 --> 00:00:52,000
Not if you stand there
and take it head-on.

